<H3> <TI>   Hepatitis Epidemic Reported in Przemysl Province </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2012173193 Warsaw TV Polonia Network in Polish 1600 GMT 20 
Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD2012173193 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw TV Polonia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hepatitis is raging in Przemysl Province. One 
person has died in the contagious diseases ward at a hospital in 
Jaroslaw, and 45 people are being hospitalized suffering of this 
viral inflammation of the liver. A state of epidemiological 
alert has been declared in the province. Self-service has been 
banned in food shops. Unpasteurized milk and its products have 
been withdrawn from sale. Sanitary measures have been stepped 
up in nurseries, schools, and canteens. 

</TEXT>

