<H3> <TI>   Containers With Radioactive Waste Seized From Ship </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY2412122593 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network in 
Portuguese 0900 GMT 24 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> PY2412122593 </F>
<F P=104>  Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Experts from the Rio Grande do Sul, RS, State 
Foundation for Environmental Protection seized 32 containers 
with clandestine radioactive waste. The cargo was transferred to 
warehouse A5 in Rio Grande Port, which was designed to store 
dangerous material. On 27 December, the experts will test the 
contents with radiation-measuring equipment and investigate the 
rest of the cargo being carried by the ship Belatrix, where the 
containers were found. 

</TEXT>

